00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:12,910
<font color="yellow">You're right in the front?</font>

423
00:31:15,153 --> 00:31:16,469
<font color="yellow">Don't come here, Jang-soo.</font>

424
00:31:16,889 --> 00:31:18,972
<font color="yellow">Go home first.</font>

425
00:31:19,330 --> 00:31:21,809
<font color="yellow">What? Why?</font>

426
00:31:22,198 --> 00:31:24,341
<font color="yellow">I want to say hi to your friends.</font>

427
00:31:24,973 --> 00:31:29,099
