00:31:29,124 --> 00:31:30,657
<font color="yellow">I said I'm really fine!</font>

429
00:31:34,299 --> 00:31:38,551
<font color="yellow">So don't come in and just go home first. Okay?</font>

430
00:31:39,875 --> 00:31:42,001
<font color="yellow">Hello? Hee-ra? She hung up already?</font>

431
00:31:43,051 --> 00:31:44,475
<font color="yellow">I'll just go by myself then.</font>

432
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:50,950
<font color="yellow">Today is a great day! Let's eat up!</font>

433
00:31:55,274 --> 00:31:56,274
<font color="yellow">Hee-ra!</font>

434
00:31:57,992 --> 00:31:58,992
<font color="yellow">Hee-ra!</font>

435
00:32:07,924 --> 00:32:08,924
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

436
00:32:09,561 --> 00:32:11,029
<font color="yellow">May I join you?</font>

437
00:32:12,204 --> 00:32:13,588
<font color="yellow">There's a seat just for me!</font>

438
00:32:15,410 --> 00:32:16,960
<font color="yellow">Hee-ra, I came pretty fast, didn't I?</font>

439
00:32:23,962 --> 00:32:26,980
<font color="yellow">So are you saying you did the right thing by</font>

440
00:32:27,005 --> 00:32:29,820
<font color="yellow">dressing like this to come see my friends?</font>

441
00:32:31,521 --> 00:32:33,299
<font color="yellow">What did I do?</font>

442
00:32:33,705 --> 00:32:35,838
<font color="yellow">And what's wrong with my outfit?</font>

443
00:32:36,324 --> 00:32:37,924
<font color="yellow">It's not like I'm naked.</font>

