445
00:32:41,482 --> 00:32:46,034
<font color="yellow">My friend Chang-ho is the branch manager of the famous global company KALMA.</font>

446
00:32:46,059 --> 00:32:50,346
<font color="yellow">My friend Mi-ryung's husband is the director of a plastic surgery hospital.</font>

447
00:32:50,577 --> 00:32:53,595
<font color="yellow">Eun-mi's husband is a prosecutor.</font>

448
00:32:56,302 --> 00:32:58,064
<font color="yellow">Now I see what you're trying to say.</font>

449
00:32:58,889 --> 00:33:03,603
<font color="yellow">So you're saying you were embarrassed by me in front of your friends.</font>

450
00:33:05,437 --> 00:33:08,525
<font color="yellow">Are you embarrassed of a no-name actor like me?</font>

451
00:33:09,733 --> 00:33:11,576
<font color="yellow">When did I say that?</font>

452
00:33:11,757 --> 00:33:13,579
<font color="yellow">That's what you were saying!</font>

453
00:33:13,604 --> 00:33:17,955
<font color="yellow">Why did you come? I told you not to come, but you ignored me and came anyways!</font>

454
00:33:17,980 --> 00:33:19,930
<font color="yellow">If you had listened to me and not came, then we</font>

