00:33:19,955 --> 00:33:21,823
<font color="yellow">wouldn't have this problem in the first place!</font>

456
00:33:22,155 --> 00:33:24,630
<font color="yellow">Oh my gosh. Are you guys fighting?</font>

457
00:33:33,881 --> 00:33:36,555
<font color="yellow">Yeah. It's about time you two had a fight.</font>

458
00:33:41,421 --> 00:33:43,020
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with my outfit?</font>

459
00:33:43,603 --> 00:33:45,610
<font color="yellow">The key of fashion is the face anyways.</font>

460
00:33:48,056 --> 00:33:49,204
<font color="yellow">Is that why she's mad?</font>

461
00:33:58,947 --> 00:34:00,287
<font color="yellow">Did I see something wrong?</font>

462
00:34:10,206 --> 00:34:11,606
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with me?</font>

463
00:34:13,785 --> 00:34:15,940
<font color="yellow">I should just go buy Hee-ra's favorite ice cream.</font>

464
00:34:33,715 --> 00:34:35,238
<font color="yellow">- Kim Mi-poong! - Oh my god!</font>

465
00:34:38,807 --> 00:34:40,797
<font color="yellow">- What were you doing all this time? - Jang-go!</font>

466
00:34:41,322 --> 00:34:43,279
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here at this hour?</font>

467
00:34:43,755 --> 00:34:45,631
<font color="yellow">You scared me!</font>

468
00:34:46,294 --> 00:34:48,576
<font color="yellow">What were you doing until this time?</font>

469
00:34:49,072 --> 00:34:50,119
<font color="yellow">You have no fear.</font>

470
00:34:50,144 --> 00:34:52,492
<font color="yellow">What if something happens to you at night?</font>

471
00:34:52,691 --> 00:34:57,403
<font color="yellow">I can protect my worry, so worry about yourself.</font>

472
00:34:58,034 --> 00:35:00,750
<font color="yellow">Do you have nothing else to do but stay here at this hour?</font>

473
00:35:00,915 --> 00:35:04,124
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong, you're going to get sick if you overwork yourself.</font>

474
00:35:04,846 --> 00:35:07,232
<font color="yellow">What kind of part-job ends at this time of night?</font>

475
00:35:08,990 --> 00:35:10,910
<font color="yellow">Why should I tell you that?</font>

476
00:35:13,752 --> 00:35:14,952
<font color="yellow">What's this smell?</font>

477
00:35:21,765 --> 00:35:23,471
<font color="yellow">Hey! Are you...</font>

478
00:35:24,781 --> 00:35:26,002
<font color="yellow">working on fishing boats?</font>

479
00:35:26,364 --> 00:35:27,364
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

480
00:35:28,035 --> 00:35:29,902
<font color="yellow">What kind of smell are you talking about?</font>

481
00:35:30,571 --> 00:35:35,994
<font color="yellow">And what is it to you if I ride a boat or a plane? Don't mind me, and just go home!</font>

482
00:35:36,275 --> 00:35:37,617
<font color="yellow">This won't do.</font>

483
00:35:38,268 --> 00:35:40,720
<font color="yellow">I understand you need to work, but you can't do this</font>

484
00:35:40,745 --> 00:35:42,965
<font color="yellow">kind of job where it ends late. Change your job.</font>

485
00:35:43,433 --> 00:35:49,483
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, you really don't have to worry about me, so don't do this.</font>

486
00:35:50,066 --> 00:35:52,223
<font color="yellow">At this rate, you're the one who will get sick.</font>

487
00:35:52,526 --> 00:35:53,601
<font color="yellow">Hurry up and go home.</font>

488
00:36:04,540 --> 00:36:06,437
<font color="yellow">What if she's really working on a fishing boat?</font>

489
00:36:08,345 --> 00:36:09,980
<font color="yellow">It can't be true.</font>

490
00:36:28,209 --> 00:36:31,771
<font color="yellow">- Mom. - Mi-poong, try this dumpling.</font>

491
00:36:33,550 --> 00:36:34,965
<font color="yellow">It's hot, so be careful.</font>

492
00:36:35,467 --> 00:36:38,422
<font color="yellow">I think we might have made too many dumplings.</font>

493
00:36:38,454 --> 00:36:40,709
<font color="yellow">I'm worried we might not be able to sell them all today.</font>

494
00:36:40,861 --> 00:36:43,928
<font color="yellow">Mom, you don't have to worry about such a thing.</font>

495
00:36:44,246 --> 00:36:46,900
<font color="yellow">These dumplings are much tastier than the ones you made yesterday.</font>

496
00:36:46,924 --> 00:36:47,991
<font color="yellow">- Really? - Yes.</font>

497
00:36:48,606 --> 00:36:51,635
<font color="yellow">The seasoning is just right, and the dumpling shell is chewy.</font>

498
00:36:51,906 --> 00:36:54,404
<font color="yellow">The dumplings are to die for.</font>

499
00:36:54,429 --> 00:36:56,647
<font color="yellow">Don't make me blush.</font>

500
00:36:56,672 --> 00:36:57,672
<font color="yellow">Eat some more.</font>

501
00:36:58,611 --> 00:37:02,995
<font color="yellow">I'm going to be late. I'm going to work now. Do your best today, too!</font>

502
00:37:03,020 --> 00:37:04,717
<font color="yellow">- Watch out for cars. - Okay.</font>

503
00:37:04,742 --> 00:37:05,846
<font color="yellow">Bye. Be safe.</font>

504
00:37:29,541 --> 00:37:31,509
<font color="yellow">Where is she going?</font>

505
00:38:25,866 --> 00:38:29,748
<font color="yellow">(We're looking for a person/ Name: Kim Dae-hoon/ Age: 67-years-old)</font>

506
00:38:29,926 --> 00:38:30,972
<font color="yellow">- Mi-poong. - Yes?</font>

507
00:38:30,997 --> 00:38:33,801
<font color="yellow">You know the fish shop in front of the market entrance, right?</font>

508
00:38:33,825 --> 00:38:36,361
<font color="yellow">Take these boxes to them quickly. They're very demanding.</font>

509
00:38:36,386 --> 00:38:37,386
<font color="yellow">Yes, all right.</font>

510
00:38:46,370 --> 00:38:49,195
<font color="yellow">- This is outrageous. So outrageous. - Oh my gosh!</font>

511
00:38:49,497 --> 00:38:52,410
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, what are you doing here?</font>

512
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:57,327
<font color="yellow">Is this the convenience part-time job you were talking about?</font>

513
00:38:57,935 --> 00:39:01,954
<font color="yellow">Oh my gosh. You're like a goblin. You appear everywhere I go and get in the way.</font>

514
00:39:03,700 --> 00:39:04,700
<font color="yellow">Let's go home.</font>

515
00:39:04,725 --> 00:39:06,690
<font color="yellow">Don't be ridiculous. Get out of the way.</font>

516
00:39:06,956 --> 00:39:09,373
<font color="yellow">I'm on my way to a delivery. I'm busy!</font>

517
00:39:09,398 --> 00:39:10,505
<font color="yellow">All right. All right.</font>

518
00:39:11,008 --> 00:39:12,008
<font color="yellow">Move.</font>

519
00:39:13,047 --> 00:39:14,224
<font color="yellow">Where do I need to go?</font>

520
00:39:14,249 --> 00:39:16,733
<font color="yellow">- Jang-go! - Weren't you in a hurry?</font>

521
00:39:17,606 --> 00:39:18,606
<font color="yellow">Where do I have to go?</font>

522
00:39:34,485 --> 00:39:35,853
<font color="yellow">How did you know I was here?</font>

523
00:39:37,239 --> 00:39:38,712
<font color="yellow">Did you follow me?</font>

524
00:39:40,850 --> 00:39:43,070
<font color="yellow">Do you think my nose is for decoration purposes only?</font>

525
00:39:45,251 --> 00:39:49,318
<font color="yellow">Why are you working here while lying to your mother about it?</font>

526
00:39:50,029 --> 00:39:51,722
<font color="yellow">It's obvious. Why would you even ask me?</font>

527
00:39:52,227 --> 00:39:55,598
<font color="yellow">This place pays you more than other places.</font>

528
00:39:56,102 --> 00:40:00,203
<font color="yellow">That shouldn't even be a reason! Even men have a hard time with this job!</font>

529
00:40:00,228 --> 00:40:02,504
<font color="yellow">Look around and see if there are any other women around!</font>

530
00:40:02,529 --> 00:40:04,972
<font color="yellow">- There are women over there! - I'm sure there are.</font>

531
00:40:05,752 --> 00:40:08,065
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, I'm strong.</font>

532
00:40:08,364 --> 00:40:09,963
<font color="yellow">I'm doing this because I can.</font>

533
00:40:10,282 --> 00:40:12,149
<font color="yellow">You keep talking back to me.</font>

534
00:40:12,285 --> 00:40:14,804
<font color="yellow">I'm not in the position to be picky about jobs right now.</font>

535
00:40:15,136 --> 00:40:19,340
<font color="yellow">I need money to make ads to find my father. I need a lot of money.</font>

536
00:40:20,099 --> 00:40:21,099
<font color="yellow">Okay, fine.</font>

537
00:40:21,645 --> 00:40:24,115
<font color="yellow">I'll tell your mother you're working at the fish market.</font>

538
00:40:24,409 --> 00:40:27,593
<font color="yellow">If she approves, I'll let you work here. That works, doesn't it?</font>

539
00:40:27,875 --> 00:40:31,081
<font color="yellow">- Jang-go! Are you really going to tell my mom? - Yes.</font>

540
00:40:31,368 --> 00:40:34,889
<font color="yellow">If you tell my mom, I'll make you bleed from both noses!</font>

541
00:40:35,036 --> 00:40:36,794
<font color="yellow">Just don't work here then!</font>

542
00:40:36,937 --> 00:40:40,795
<font color="yellow">Didn't you hear what I said? I'm not in that kind of position right now!</font>

543
00:40:40,820 --> 00:40:42,811
<font color="yellow">Are you listening to me or not?</font>

544
00:40:43,436 --> 00:40:44,703
<font color="yellow">Don't work here!</font>

545
00:40:57,589 --> 00:40:59,208
<font color="yellow">Oh my gosh!</font>

546
00:40:59,748 --> 00:41:01,992
<font color="yellow">If you were my sister, I would have beaten you up.</font>

547
00:41:07,589 --> 00:41:11,195
<font color="yellow">Hello, sir! Yes, I'm on my way! Bye!</font>

548
00:41:11,402 --> 00:41:14,627
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, I'm begging you! Please!</font>

549
00:41:14,841 --> 00:41:19,249
<font color="yellow">You can never tell my mom! Never! You can never tell her!</font>

550
00:41:49,158 --> 00:41:50,182
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

551
00:41:51,501 --> 00:41:52,599
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

552
00:41:56,398 --> 00:42:00,320
<font color="yellow">Mister, please find my father for me.</font>

553
00:42:01,865 --> 00:42:04,198
<font color="yellow">My father's name is Kim Deok-cheon.</font>

554
00:42:04,858 --> 00:42:07,267
<font color="yellow">My father lives in Seoul.</font>

555
00:42:09,692 --> 00:42:11,466
<font color="yellow">Then what's your name?</font>

556
00:42:12,016 --> 00:42:14,849
<font color="yellow">My name is Kim Dae-hoon.</font>

557
00:42:18,176 --> 00:42:20,443
<font color="yellow">Should I buy you that steamed bun?</font>

558
00:42:21,995 --> 00:42:22,995
<font color="yellow">Yes!</font>

559
00:42:23,423 --> 00:42:26,431
<font color="yellow">- Let's go inside. - Thank you.</font>

560
00:42:35,104 --> 00:42:37,333
<font color="yellow">(Store Contract)</font>

561
00:42:39,291 --> 00:42:40,291
<font color="yellow">What's this?</font>

562
00:42:41,482 --> 00:42:42,615
<font color="yellow">A store contract.</font>

563
00:42:44,678 --> 00:42:47,672
<font color="yellow">I looked for it urgently, but it's quite nice. The location is great, and</font>

564
00:42:47,697 --> 00:42:50,488
<font color="yellow">it's near here, too. Also, it's empty, so you can open up right away.</font>

565
00:42:51,209 --> 00:42:53,209
<font color="yellow">Why are you giving this to me?</font>

566
00:42:54,773 --> 00:42:58,072
<font color="yellow">I thought it would be nice if you and Mi-poong opened up your own business.</font>

567
00:42:59,455 --> 00:43:03,501
<font color="yellow">I was thinking about it, and you can open up a store that sells side dishes or...</font>

568
00:43:03,865 --> 00:43:06,224
<font color="yellow">Oh! You're good at making dumpling soup. You can</font>

569
00:43:06,249 --> 00:43:08,366
<font color="yellow">sell dumplings. What do you think?</font>

570
00:43:09,887 --> 00:43:15,209
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, did you discuss this with Mi-poong already?</font>

571
00:43:18,015 --> 00:43:19,015
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

572
00:43:20,475 --> 00:43:23,324
<font color="yellow">You know what she's like. Do you think she'll accept this?</font>

573
00:43:25,261 --> 00:43:26,594
<font color="yellow">Then I can't either.</font>

574
00:43:28,380 --> 00:43:30,716
<font color="yellow">How can I accept something she doesn't know about?</font>

575
00:43:32,134 --> 00:43:36,825
<font color="yellow">Thank you, but take it back.</font>

576
00:43:39,705 --> 00:43:41,505
<font color="yellow">I didn't know you would do this.</font>

577
00:43:42,959 --> 00:43:46,074
<font color="yellow">If I tell you this, Mi-poong will make me bleed from both noses.</font>

578
00:43:48,563 --> 00:43:49,563
<font color="yellow">Mother.</font>

579
00:43:51,293 --> 00:43:54,391
<font color="yellow">You didn't know Mi-poong works at the fish market, do you?</font>

580
00:43:55,487 --> 00:43:56,487
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

581
00:43:59,769 --> 00:44:02,237
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong works at the fish market?</font>

582
00:44:02,991 --> 00:44:03,991
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

583
00:44:04,274 --> 00:44:06,575
<font color="yellow">It's hard for even men to do.</font>

584
00:44:07,096 --> 00:44:10,032
<font color="yellow">No matter how many times I tell her to quit, she won't listen to me.</font>

585
00:44:10,763 --> 00:44:12,181
<font color="yellow">That's why I came to you.</font>

586
00:44:13,914 --> 00:44:15,209
<font color="yellow">Please take this.</font>

587
00:44:17,757 --> 00:44:21,318
<font color="yellow">If you feel uncomfortable taking it, just think of it as alimony.</font>

588
00:44:22,223 --> 00:44:24,977
<font color="yellow">It would be terrible if she got hurt while doing such hard labor.</font>

589
00:44:26,242 --> 00:44:27,242
<font color="yellow">Mother.</font>

590
00:44:33,126 --> 00:44:36,102
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, thank you.</font>

591
00:44:37,753 --> 00:44:41,117
<font color="yellow">I feel ashamed, but I'll accept it gratefully.</font>

592
00:44:41,916 --> 00:44:47,474
<font color="yellow">And I'll make sure to work hard and pay you back with interest.</font>

593
00:44:48,095 --> 00:44:50,095
<font color="yellow">So you're accepting it, right?</font>

594
00:44:51,058 --> 00:44:52,913
<font color="yellow">I should go before you change your mind.</font>

595
00:44:53,573 --> 00:44:57,596
<font color="yellow">Mother, please make sure Mi-poong won't come see me with this contract.</font>

596
00:44:58,194 --> 00:44:59,394
<font color="yellow">I'll be going now!</font>

597
00:45:02,335 --> 00:45:03,335
<font color="yellow">Bye!</font>

598
00:45:19,381 --> 00:45:23,782
<font color="yellow">Grandfather, you're going to get really sick at this rate.</font>

599
00:45:24,580 --> 00:45:27,504
<font color="yellow">What will I do if something happens to you, too?</font>

600
00:45:28,150 --> 00:45:30,240
<font color="yellow">You need strength in order to find dad.</font>

601
00:45:31,097 --> 00:45:32,589
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

602
00:45:48,420 --> 00:45:51,394
<font color="yellow">What if someone kidnapped Dae-hoon?</font>

603
00:45:54,013 --> 00:45:55,013
<font color="yellow">Kidnap?</font>

604
00:45:55,038 --> 00:45:57,394
<font color="yellow">Yes, kidnap!</font>

605
00:45:57,767 --> 00:46:01,995
<font color="yellow">Otherwise, why would we not be able to find him?</font>

