<font color="yellow">You gave it to her as alimony anyways, so it's all over now.</font>

805
01:00:13,019 --> 01:00:15,798
<font color="yellow">So back off her now.</font>

806
01:00:16,076 --> 01:00:18,077
<font color="yellow">Don't go anywhere near her.</font>

807
01:00:18,872 --> 01:00:21,227
<font color="yellow">End it with the alimony. Got it?</font>

808
01:00:56,736 --> 01:00:58,274
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, mother.</font>

809
01:00:59,275 --> 01:01:00,608
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Mi-poong.</font>

810
01:01:00,794 --> 01:01:01,794
<font color="yellow">Jang-go.</font>

811
01:01:03,617 --> 01:01:04,684
<font color="yellow">We need to talk.</font>

812
01:01:14,546 --> 01:01:16,613
<font color="yellow">(Father's Dumplings)</font>

813
01:01:20,420 --> 01:01:21,420
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

814
01:01:23,904 --> 01:01:25,153
<font color="yellow">I'll apologize on her behalf.</font>

815
01:01:27,547 --> 01:01:29,776
<font color="yellow">My mother won't come back here ever again.</font>

816
01:01:31,237 --> 01:01:32,536
<font color="yellow">You're very angry, aren't you?</font>

817
01:01:36,238 --> 01:01:39,269
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, I'm not angry.</font>

818
01:01:41,071 --> 01:01:44,391
<font color="yellow">And I don't want to fight with you about things like this anymore.</font>

819
01:01:46,376 --> 01:01:51,956
<font color="yellow">I'll make sure to work hard and do whatever I can to pay you back.</font>

820
01:01:52,987 --> 01:01:54,306
<font color="yellow">Why are you talking that way?</font>

821
01:01:55,926 --> 01:01:57,401
<font color="yellow">Why can't you realize my feelings?</font>

822
01:01:57,639 --> 01:01:59,013
<font color="yellow">What will happen if I do?</font>

823
01:02:00,402 --> 01:02:03,050
<font color="yellow">You saw what your mother did earlier.</font>

824
01:02:05,793 --> 01:02:06,993
<font color="yellow">We won't work out.</font>

825
01:02:09,308 --> 01:02:12,386
<font color="yellow">You do know our court appointment is coming up soon, right?</font>

826
01:02:14,215 --> 01:02:15,948
<font color="yellow">We'll see each other then.</font>

827
01:02:17,564 --> 01:02:21,372
<font color="yellow">And don't come back here ever again.</font>

828
01:02:47,710 --> 01:02:51,972
<font color="yellow">Ma'am, did you see a man with white hair wearing glasses?</font>

829
01:03:51,516 --> 01:03:55,531
<font color="yellow">- Where are you going? - I'm going to Seoul. Give me a ride. Please?</font>

830
01:04:35,984 --> 01:04:39,459
<font color="yellow">Go away!</font>

831
01:04:39,484 --> 01:04:40,951
<font color="yellow">Oh, that awful stench!</font>

832
01:04:41,158 --> 01:04:45,461
<font color="yellow">Business isn't doing well either! My goodness!</font>

833
01:04:46,326 --> 01:04:47,326
<font color="yellow">Go away!</font>

834
01:04:55,401 --> 01:04:56,401
<font color="yellow">Father...</font>

835
01:04:59,330 --> 01:05:01,134
<font color="yellow">Mother...</font>

836
01:05:16,637 --> 01:05:18,978
<font color="yellow">Mother...</font>

837
01:05:37,419 --> 01:05:40,087
<font color="yellow">(Father's Dumplings)</font>

838
01:06:36,030 --> 01:06:37,030
<font color="yellow">It's hot!</font>

839
01:06:38,381 --> 01:06:39,381
<font color="yellow">Father...?</font>

840
01:06:40,399 --> 01:06:42,028
<font color="yellow">Father! Father!</font>

841
01:06:42,710 --> 01:06:43,710
<font color="yellow">Father!</font>

842
01:06:45,986 --> 01:06:47,119
<font color="yellow">What did she say?</font>

843
01:06:47,406 --> 01:06:48,406
<font color="yellow">It's hot!</font>

844
01:06:48,834 --> 01:06:53,647
<font color="yellow">Father! Father!</font>

845
01:06:54,623 --> 01:06:59,008
<font color="yellow">- Father! - Dae-hoon!</font>

846
01:07:16,505 --> 01:07:18,104
<font color="yellow">(Blow Breeze)</font>

847
01:07:18,239 --> 01:07:24,302
<font color="yellow">- That was your father, wasn't it? - It was him! He was right in front of my eyes!</font>

848
01:07:24,327 --> 01:07:26,487
<font color="yellow">Hurry up and open this!</font>

849
01:07:29,003 --> 01:07:30,419
<font color="yellow">Yes, that's right!</font>

850
01:07:32,913 --> 01:07:35,414
<font color="yellow">Hey! You crazy woman!</font>

851
01:07:35,695 --> 01:07:38,563
<font color="yellow">They bought those dumplings from Mi-poong's dumpling store!</font>

852
01:07:39,041 --> 01:07:40,041
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

853
01:07:40,066 --> 01:07:41,448
<font color="yellow">What is he talking about?</font>

854
01:07:41,901 --> 01:07:44,775
<font color="yellow">- You told me to come out! - Why are you making things up?</font>

855
01:07:45,766 --> 01:07:47,017
<font color="yellow">Listen to me carefully.</font>

856
01:07:47,661 --> 01:07:50,192
<font color="yellow">I'm going to tell grandfather and lock you up in the hospital.</font>

857
01:07:50,217 --> 01:07:51,983
<font color="yellow">How can you do this to me?</font>

858
01:07:52,008 --> 01:07:53,981
<font color="yellow">I'm scared, father.</font>

859
01:07:54,338 --> 01:07:56,152
<font color="yellow">Please go your way!</font>

860
01:07:56,336 --> 01:07:58,514
<font color="yellow">Kim Mi-poong, I can't live without you.</font>

861
01:07:59,076 --> 01:08:00,925
<font color="yellow">I don't want to see you ever again.</font>

